quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,"“Soni E ŵandu ŵangu! Ligongo chichi une ngum’bilanjila jenumanja ku chokoko, sano jenumanja ni nkumilanjila une ku Moto!”"
  40,42,"“Nkumilanjila une kuti nankaane Allah ni nam’bwanganye Jwalakwe ni ichindu yanganingola nayo umanyilisi, kutendaga une ngum’bilanjila ku (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakululuka kusyene!”"
  40,43,"“Pangali kaichila yanti ŵankumilan’jila kuti nagalagatilejeo, nganakola duwa (janti mpaka ajijanje) pa duniya namuno ku Akhera, soni kuti kwakuujila kwetu ni kwa Allah, soni kuti ŵakupelenganya malile (pakonanga) ni ŵatachiŵa ŵandu ŵa ku Moto.”"
  40,44,"“Basi tinchiyikumbuchila yangunsalilayi, ni ngwegamisya indu yangu kwa Allah. Chisimu Allah ni Jwakwalolechesya achikapolo (Ŵakwe).”"
  40,45,"Basi Allah ni ŵan’gosile ku yakusakala ya malindi gaŵantendele, ni yasyungwile ŵandu ŵa Firiauna ilagasyo yakusakala nnope"
  40,46,"Moto, akulosyedwa ŵanganyao ku walakweo kundaŵi ni kwigulo (m’malembe mwao). Sano lisiku lyajichijima Kiyama (kuchiŵechetedwa yanti): “Mwajinjisyani ŵandu ŵa Firiauna ku ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope.”"
  40,47,"Soni (mwakumbusyani) katema katachikanganaga m’Moto. Basi nitachiti ŵangalikombolela kwa aŵala ŵaŵalikwesyisye: “Chisimu uwwe twaliji akunkuya ŵenu, ana jenumanja ni chintutyochesye upande wine wa Moto?”"
  40,48,"Aŵala ŵaŵalikwesyisye ni tachiti: “Chisimu uwwe wosope ŵene tuli mwemuno, chisimu Allah pamasile paajiileenye chilikati cha achikapolo (Ŵakwe).”"
  40,49,"Aŵala ŵatachiŵa m’Moto tachiti pakwasalila akujisunga Jahannama (Achimalaika): “Mum’bendani M’mbuje gwenu (Allah) kuti atupunguchisye uwwe ilagasyo lisiku limpepe.”"
  40,50,"(Akujisunga Jahannama) tachiti: “Ana achimitenga ŵenu nganaŵa nkum’bichilila ni ilosyo yakuonechela?” Ŵanganyao tachiti: “Elo.” (Akujisunga Jahannama) tachiti: “Basi wombani.” Ni nganijiŵa duwa jamakafili ikaŵeje mu kusokonechela"
  40,51,Chisimu Uwwe chitwachenjele Achimitenga Ŵetu kwisa soni aŵala ŵakulupilile pa umi wa duniya ni lisiku lyasichijima mboni (lisiku lya Kiyama)
  40,52,"Lisiku lyaangaakamuchisya ŵalupuso kuliŵalanga kwao, ni tachikola ŵanganyao malweso, ni tachikola soni nyumba jakusakala nnope (Jahannama)"
  40,53,"Soni chisimu chene Musa twampele chongoko, ni twapele ŵanache ŵa Israila kuchitawalila Chitabu (Taurat)"
  40,54,(Chachaliji) chongolo kwisa soni chikumbusyo kwa ŵakwete lunda
  40,55,"Basi pililani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), chisimu chilanga cha Allah chakuonaonape, soni ŵendani chikululuko ku sambi syenu, ni nnuswejesyeje lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) kwigulo ni kundaŵi"
  40,56,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakukangana pa ma Ȃya ga Allah mwangali umboni uliose wawayichilile, m’mitima mwao mwangali ikaŵeje kulikwesya, (akusosa ukulu wakumpunda Muhammadi ﷺ) nambo nganaŵa aŵuŵiche ŵanganyao, basi lijuyani mwa Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakulolechesya"
  40,57,"Chisimu gumba mawunde ni mataka kuŵele kwekulungwa nnope kupunda gumba ŵandu, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ngaakumanyilila"
  40,58,"Soni nganaŵa alandene jwangalola ni jwakulolaga, namuno aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone (nganaŵa alandene) ni akusakasya. Yannonope ni yankukumbuchilaga"
  40,59,"Chisimu Kiyama jikwisa kwene, jangali kaikasya (yakwika kwakwe), nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ngaakukulupilila"
  40,60,"Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni akuti: “Mumombani Une tinan’janje. Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulikwesya pakuleka kungalagatila Une, tachijinjila ku Jahannama ali ŵakunyosyeka.”"
  40,61,"Allah ni Ajula jwam’bichile chilo kuti ntulalilejemo, muusi nikuŵa wakuloleka, chisimu Allah ni Nsyene umbone wakwatendela ŵandu, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ŵangatogolela"
  40,62,"Jwalakwe ni Allah M’mbuje gwenu, Nkugumba chindu chilichose, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, ana nkugalausyidwa chinauli (kuleka yakuona)"
  40,63,Iyyoyopeyo ni yaŵatite pakugalausyidwa aŵala ŵaŵaliji nkugakanila ma Ȃya ga Allah (kalakala)
  40,64,"Allah ni Ajula jwantendele litaka kuŵa lyakutamilichika, liwunde nikuŵa nsakasa, ni ampaanjiile kaoneche kenu, basi ni akakolosyisye kaoneche kenuko, ni ampele ichindu yambone, Jwalakwe ni Allah M’mbuje gwenu, basi anyakwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) Allah, M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"
  40,65,"Jwalakwe ni Jwaumi wandamo, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, basi mum’bombani Jwalakwe mwakunswejechesya dini Jakwe. Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah, M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"